# Modular (internachi/modular)

- This is a modular application. Each module lives in its own directory under `app-modules/`.
- Read and follow `.cursor/skills/modular/SKILL.md` before creating or changing module code.
- Use `ddev artisan make:* --module={module}` for module components.
- Run `php artisan modules:sync` after adding modules or changing module structure.
